Name: 1,3-dichloropropene to generic market for pesticide, unspecified | pesticide, unspecified | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/20:Manufacture of chemicals and chemical products/201:Manufacture of basic chemicals, fertilizers and nitrogen compounds, plastics/2011:Manufacture of basic chemicals
Description: 1,3-dichloropropene is used as a pesticide in the United States, Europe, Japan, the Philippines, and Africa. It is phased out in the EU (http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/site/en/oj/2007/l_249/l_24920070925en00110013.pdf).
